        "created_at": "2020-12-03T19:15:58.327Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019ll definitely report back based on the performance/any oddities I\u2019m seeing, and I\u2019ll give the Docker route a try as well. Although I don\u2019t have a ton of time resources available, as soon as the development crunch phase ends in a few months, I\u2019ll gladly accept your help getting a larger-scale Mac cluster properly tested, <em>for science!</em></p>\n<p>(You\u2019d think Apple stewarding the project would be more interested than me in playing around with this, but I guess that would be all hush hush even if it were happening <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/twitter/upside_down_face.png?v=9\" title=\":upside_down_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":upside_down_face:\">)</p>",
